@Shutter: I could not disagree more about Jewelcrafting, it is by far the most lucrative profession in WoW at the moment(certainly on my server). I have made over 20,000 gold to date pretty much just from JewelCrafting.
The method&#039;s i use for doing this are quite simple: 1) Buy stacks of adamantite ore off the AH 2) Prospect into gems. 3) Vend all the green-quality gems and powder 4) Cut the blue-quality gems into the current best seller of that colour 5) Profit.
For an example i bought 1000g of ore on Sunday morning. Today i have 1500g worth of completed auctions in my mailbox. Obvisouly it varies depending on your servers market. I also made 3500g in a week just by saving up gems to sell when the season 3 gear hit.
